Method Detail

addCoordinate

public void addCoordinate(Coordinate c)
Adds a coordinate to the data set. It adjusts the min and max values if the point added is lower or higher than the existing minimums or maximums.

If using a maximum number of points, it assumes that the x's coming in are monotonically increasing.

Parameters:
c - The coordinate to add.
